{"tid":1025292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華南理工大學涉篡改考生複試成績    其中小組面試第一名曾被改為不及格","createTime":"2019-02-17T08:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T08:52:28.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"baf818f3842ffe7cde6f2db490a2c469898b9fd9","tid":1025292,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T08:50:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190216/s00004/93d3658fd3f34135b8e76c6cb585ea3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190216%2Fs00004%2F93d3658fd3f34135b8e76c6cb585ea3c.jpg&h=2263deda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華南理工大學8名報讀研究生的考生面試成績疑被篡改，其中小組面試第一名的考試曾被改為不及格，4名涉事教職員現時被校方停職調查。<br />\n<br />\n有網民周一（11日）發帖舉報，在華南理工大學的計算機科學與工程學院2018年碩士研究生複試招生期間，計算機學院院長、研究生招生小組組長張軍召集黨委書記練偉傑、紀委書記楊毅仁，以及副院長余志文等4人，曾直接篡改8名考生的複試面試成績，有5人被調高成績後獲錄取，3人面試成績則被改低後落選。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名複試成績原為小組第一的學生，修改分數後被改為不及格，未被校方錄取，惟該學生向學校投訴後又被改分錄取。<br />\n<br />\n華南理工大學新聞中心於14日晚發聲明回應稱，已於13日成立工作組展開調查，絕不容忍任何違反招生制度與紀律行為，一經證實，將依法嚴肅處理事件。目前，涉事4人已停職並接受調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8/article/20190216/s00004/1550301276648/%E6%B6%89%E7%AF%A1%E6%94%B9%E8%80%83%E7%94%9F%E8%A4%87%E8%A9%A6%E6%88%90%E7%B8%BE-%E8%8F%AF%E5%8D%97%E7%90%86%E5%B7%A54%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E9%81%AD%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E5%81%9C%E8%81%B7%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B2%25B8%2Farticle%2F20190216%2Fs00004%2F1550301276648%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E7%25AF%25A1%25E6%2594%25B9%25E8%2580%2583%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A4%2587%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25B8%25BE-%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25B7%25A54%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2581%259C%25E8%2581%25B7%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxrJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=45888615\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B2%25B8%2Farticle%2F20190216%2Fs00004%2F1550301276648%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E7%25AF%25A1%25E6%2594%25B9%25E8%2580%2583%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A4%2587%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25B8%25BE-%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25B7%25A54%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2581%259C%25E8%2581%25B7%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5&h=da4bb53a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8/article/20190216/s00004/1550301276648/%E6%B6%89%E7%AF%A1%E6%94%B9%E8%80%83%E7%94%9F%E8%A4%87%E8%A9%A6%E6%88%90%E7%B8%BE-%E8%8F%AF%E5%8D%97%E7%90%86%E5%B7%A54%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E9%81%AD%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E5%81%9C%E8%81%B7%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5</a>"},{"pid":"c57c6ceb3a675cd3ac4cd0550bad22deec66c180","tid":1025292,"uid":119145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T08:52:28.000Z","msg":"幾時到香港理工大學"}]}